* This is a read-only file. User-specified tunables are stored
* in usr/sysgen/stune.

* oplocks_enabled ==> indicates whether oplocks are enabled.
* oplock_timeout ==> time in secods for a proccess to sleep while waiting
*			for an oplocked to be revoked.
*			
* name			default      	minimum		maximum

oplocks_enabled		1		0		1
oplock_timeout		30		1		1000
